{"tid":621261,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]電腦有問題","createTime":"2018-04-08T07:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T08:19:37.000Z","uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8625d63347da18f8df5ec074a80c850c39204710","tid":621261,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"上星期開始，部腦閒置一陣便會hang機，鍵盤滑鼠無反應，要按電源掣熄機。<br />\n<br />\n部腦上個月尾喺T記買，開頭幾日都無事，之後做過幾樣嘢，唔知關唔關事：<br />\n更新過Win10 1709<br />\n自己加咗張舊顯示卡MSI 1060 6G<br />\n自己加咗個舊HDD WD 1TB<br />\n<br />\n上網查吓，之後在電源設定將電腦set用「高效能」，仲衰，用用下都hang機。<br />\n然後試吓改做「省電模式」就正常，用幾個鐘都無hang機了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日拆走個舊HDD，在電源設定set用「標準」，點知用用下就自動重新開機。<br />\n改返「省電模式」又無事，唔通係電源問題？<br />\n<br />\n原本配置：<br />\nAMD Ryzen&trade; 5 2400G 3.2GHz 4M L3 4 Core 8 Thread 65W AM4<br />\nASUS PRIME B350M-A AM4 M.ATX <br />\nToshiba DT01ACA100 1TB 7200rpm 32MB 3.5 Inch HDD <br />\nG.Skill DDR4 Aegis Gaming Series 3000MHz 1x8GB F4-3000C16S-8GISB  <br />\nIntel SSD 760P Series M.2 80mm PCIe NVMe 3.1 x4 256GB <br />\nAntec High Current Gamer Series HCG-520M 80Plus Bronze 520W Semi Modular \t<br />\nCorsair 100R Window ATX Case<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得問題喺邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf939893605cb5f98b9f4b85479a18bffb797aa","tid":621261,"uid":76527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"成部抬返去試"},{"pid":"9733871350abbfb521712c9d5e8b5fb033a2ce5f","tid":621261,"uid":179672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"咪搵返間野搞，你期望我地可以點幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe0756de97e9f7b4d28737986b790fad194a26f","tid":621261,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:36:37.000Z","msg":"散熱裝得唔好?"},{"pid":"faf2068bb4870348c3b12bdea9b49fc584f88a86","tid":621261,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成部抬返去試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好重呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412b7b147bda986e485bf99c1b7a42ecb065c949","tid":621261,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪搵返間野搞，你期望我地可以點幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會問間嘢，但我見連登多高手嘛，咪問吓"},{"pid":"eaf9e6197283724267598a7bc6d7f45442ec051d","tid":621261,"uid":121673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"有冇試過 update BIOS?"},{"pid":"95c76469300ecafa392ac581a4e62f879deff93c","tid":621261,"uid":76527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"其實硬件都係逐樣試，你怕重就自己排除晒所有可能。<br />\n<br />\n拎走display card玩一排會唔會hang，<br />\n拎走HDD睇下會唔會hang,<br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁仲麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fb7059f286d7adbf8884e9f73ac99de16ff4cb","tid":621261,"uid":117978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"window 10係用用下會lag，軟件問題"},{"pid":"4f264c59cdf5e3569ebb89be1fbcb33463291c2e","tid":621261,"uid":179672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"412b7b147bda986e485bf99c1b7a42ecb065c949","tid":621261,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪搵返間野搞，你期望我地可以點幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會問間嘢，但我見連登多高手嘛，咪問吓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"見你一開始咁講，都係冇咩呢方面既知識<br />\n亂咁聽人講亂試，不如拎返去鋪頭俾人搞算啦<br />\n一陣愈試愈亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5e6157f174672b84eaf46ff66c20aaa1817bab","tid":621261,"uid":181129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:05:49.000Z","msg":"1。check下cpu散熱有冇裝好<br />\n2.  係塊板用jumpet reset bios<br />\n3. 如果有內置display就remove張display卡<br />\n4.  check下event monitor有冇error"},{"pid":"4786ae09e0bdc61df994113f7053afbb78308621","tid":621261,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"T記唔係有售後咩？ 部機佢哋砌嘅<br />\n叫返佢哋處理好啲喎"},{"pid":"3b05c36f9489f0593544d81d7a187aa4ff1102d0","tid":621261,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T02:30:42.000Z","msg":"同埋我記得ryzen底板對intel 760p相容性唔係好好<br />\n換其他ssd 可能可以改善問題"},{"pid":"6f768e4ad474c7fb90a66ed5a1759f2ca3e3538e","tid":621261,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴打<br />\n<br />\n我發現好似係屋企個拖板其中一個插位壞壞地，呢家我換咗就無問題出現了<br />\n<br />\n等我觀察多一兩先<br />\n<br />\n唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}